{"tid":2497176,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國核電站放射物排放上限　遠超日本福島十倍","createTime":"2021-04-20T10:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T10:45:56.000Z","uid":261647,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c72dc0606e0ab40f11726096f369cd4ccc685616","tid":2497176,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/5331334796940995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fposts%2F5331334796940995&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJw4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=90f69f9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/5331334796940995</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUxoTPh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUxoTPh.jpg&h=d8a9c543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怍者：自由亞洲粵語 RFA Cantonese<br />\n<br />\n【港媒：中國核電站放射物排放上限遠超福島十倍】<br />\n<br />\n日本決定把福島核電廠污水傾倒到太平洋，被北京批評不顧亞太多數國家人民利益和環境保護，不惜犧牲他國民眾和自然環境。香港《眾新聞》周三（14日）翻查中國官方的資料，發現中國現存的49座核電機組，都有將核廢水傾倒進大海。距離香港只有50公里的大亞灣核電站，放射性物質「氚」的排放上限，比日本福島的排放標準高出十倍。"},{"pid":"18fb41d3e1b19076cb480cc7760177a0227434d8","tid":2497176,"uid":62721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"中國人吃這套"},{"pid":"a7f07eebf453d5cbb09432b75555b90c0a69bfa3","tid":2497176,"uid":48362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"任何設施 只要由中國人建造<br />\n你就知道 這些設施極度危險 破壞環境<br />\n和危害所有人類的安全"},{"pid":"d15968061e03129b024ec18d4b74830fe2bee809","tid":2497176,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186425a2ead5564e9f4d72bd4154ce41b5bc92d3","tid":2497176,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,